works.complaint:
Dear Sirs

We act on behalf of Mr Pankaj Oswal.

Our client recently took action against YouTube who permanently removed a 

video which contained material that was defamatory of and concerning our  

client.

The purpose of this letter is to advise you that a reference or extract of
 
this material remains in Google's information set.

The URL in question is: www.youtube.com/watch?v=-CNncbq_-pE

The heading of the link is: Pankaj Oswal (Burrup Fertilisers) on Today  
Tonight - YouTube

The precise words that appear are: "1 March 2011 - Burrup Fertilisers ex  

owner doing what he does best, spinning complete and utter B.S If you come
 
back to Australia Pankaj, bring your vasoline..."

This material is offensive and defamatory and obviously actionable by our 

client.  YouTube took immediate action to deal with this and we ask that  

Google treat this material with the same level of seriousness and urgency.


We hereby demand that the link to the URL  
www.youtube.com/watch?v=-CNncbq_-pE be permanently removed from Google's  

information set by close of business AEST Friday 8 June 2012 failing which
 
we will revert to our client for instructions to take immediate action
with  
further notice to Google.
